    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS EATON RTLO SERIES - INSTALL - FRONT AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="2">
        <title>FRONT AUXILIARY DRIVE GEAR</title>
        <para>Make sure the splitter yoke bar setscrew hole aligns with the yoke setscrew hole.</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Place the shift yoke in splitter sliding clutch slot. Install the clutch and yoke on the
                splitter yoke bar (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017l8">Figure 218</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017l8" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017l8" filename="../figg13/G13017L8.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 218. Clutch &#38; Yoke On Splitter Bar</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the setscrew and tighten to 35 to 45 ft-lbs. (47 to 61 N&#8226;m) of torque (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13017l9">Figure 219</hotlnk>). Lockwire securely.
            </para>
            <figure id="f13017l9" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13017l9" filename="../figg13/G13017L9.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 219. Install Setscrew</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
